import { styled } from "styled-components";

const Container = styled.div``
const ProductList = () => {
    return (
      <Container>
        <Navbar />
        <Announcement />
        <Title>Dresses</Title>
        <FilterContainer>
          <Filter>
            <FilterText>Filter Products:</FilterText>
            <Select>
              <Option disabled selected>
                Color
              </Option>
              <Option>White</Option>
              <Option>Black</Option>
              <Option>Red</Option>
              <Option>Blue</Option>
              <Option>Yellow</Option>
              <Option>Green</Option>
            </Select>
            <Select>
              <Option disabled selected>
                Size
              </Option>
              <Option>XS</Option>
              <Option>S</Option>
              <Option>M</Option>
              <Option>L</Option>
              <Option>XL</Option>
            </Select>
          </Filter>
          <Filter>
            <FilterText>Sort Products:</FilterText>
            <Select>
              <Option selected>Newest</Option>
              <Option>Price (asc)</Option>
              <Option>Price (desc)</Option>
            </Select>
          </Filter>
        </FilterContainer>
        <Products />
        <Newsletter />
        <Footer />
      </Container>
    );
  };
  
  export default ProductList;
